            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Seduction is the subtle art of weaving charm and influence through words, glances, and gestures. It\u2019s the skill of turning a stranger\u2019s guard into trust with a well-timed compliment or coaxing a tightly held secret from a wary rival with a disarming smile. Mastery lies in reading the unspoken\u2014sensing desires, fears, and weaknesses\u2014and knowing just when to press or pull back. Yet, it\u2019s a perilous craft; a single misstep can unravel the illusion, sparking anger or betrayal where trust once bloomed. Those who wield seduction walk a fine line, their charisma a quiet blade, sharp and precise.",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          }
